    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.工藝的本質與內涵<br>2.工藝設計的範圍<br>3.工藝材質、工具及技法<br>4.工藝設計方法<br>5.工藝設計的發展<br>6.工藝設計綜合創作<br>",
        "en": "1.The craft of essence and connotation<br>2.The craft of scope <br>3.The craft of materials, tools and techniques<br>4.The craft design method<br>5.The craft design development<br>6.The craft design creation<br>"
